###  http://www.ppgi.uniriotec.br/CyberSecSys_1.0#Risk_Analysis_and_Assessment
:Risk_Analysis_and_Assessment rdf:type owl:Class ;
                              rdfs:subClassOf :Process_Approach .


###  http://www.ppgi.uniriotec.br/CyberSecSys_1.0#Risk_and_Threat_Assessment
:Risk_and_Threat_Assessment rdf:type owl:Class ;
                            rdfs:subClassOf :Process_Component .


###  http://www.ppgi.uniriotec.br/CyberSecSys_1.0#Security_Component
:Security_Component rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.ppgi.uniriotec.br/CyberSecSys_1.0#Security_Performance_Validation
:Security_Performance_Validation rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                 rdfs:subClassOf :Process_PerformanceEvaluation .


###  http://www.ppgi.uniriotec.br/CyberSecSys_1.0#Standardization_and_Quality
:Standardization_and_Quality rdf:type owl:Class ;
                             rdfs:subClassOf :Technology_Approach .


###  http://www.ppgi.uniriotec.br/CyberSecSys_1.0#SystemOfSystems_Component
:SystemOfSystems_Component rdf:type owl:Class .


